{"tid":2315629,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★醫管局：第四波疫情有不少嚴重個案都較年輕","createTime":"2020-12-07T10:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T12:07:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"05e7d6d79638795598da06bbee2ec0db73b091e0","tid":2315629,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:09:52.000Z","msg":"一般患者直至十分差的情況，即使用呼吸機亦無法維持血氧在安全水平，才會使用人工心肺機，而使用這個儀器的風險都很高。他提到，外國相關的新冠肺炎患者，倘使用人工心肺後死亡率達50%。他承認，本港的嚴重患者，在今波疫情中有年輕化的趨勢，「臨床上的觀察，令人非常擔心<br />\n<br />\n有年輕患者個案呼吸系統有困難，要用呼吸機，甚至用人工肺，而死亡率更達30%至40%，當中不只是年長人士，故提醒所有人要小心。他又形容，今次不少患者送院後病情已非常嚴重，「一嚟就要急救措施，呢一波病毒株係危險嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/558340/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0-%E5%BC%B5%E6%95%AC%E8%BB%92%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E5%B8%B6%E4%BD%8D%E5%93%A1%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B0%E5%A4%9A5%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E9%99%BD%E6%80%A7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F558340%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E6%2595%25AC%25E8%25BB%2592%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%2594%25B1%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%25A4%259A5%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E9%2599%25BD%25E6%2580%25A7&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTjY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=88e7aeb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/558340/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0-%E5%BC%B5%E6%95%AC%E8%BB%92%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E5%B8%B6%E4%BD%8D%E5%93%A1%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B0%E5%A4%9A5%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E9%99%BD%E6%80%A7</a>"},{"pid":"fef52ae2372843fa8e89b59fd1eacf280522a66a","tid":2315629,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:10:17.000Z","msg":"一名在伊利沙伯醫院工作的醫生，確診新冠肺炎後，病情轉差，昨天轉入深切治療部，現時需插喉。伊院近日有2名病理科醫生確診，分別是一名45歲男子和一名33歲男子。據了解，危殆的是45歲的男醫生。<br />\n<br />\n該名45歲組織病理學醫生，11月26後沒有上班，他於11月27日起出現病徵。不過，他較早前曾與一名同事（33歲男醫生）下班時一同坐港鐵，而該名同事其後亦確診。醫院管理局早前指，二人不需接觸病人，在化驗室工作時亦不需接觸新冠病毒樣本，推斷不是在院內感染。"},{"pid":"d1e66da70fff73809d438e026323f7921cfdb2c1","tid":2315629,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKKanHO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKKanHO.jpg&h=43ed8a7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"504243ee27b926a63d90fb5a08bab9ab133bb829","tid":2315629,"uid":8014,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:20:52.000Z","msg":"廿幾歲都係未撚驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\njust a flu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd111ec2007a9184d71446ed837d2490d1a1abe","tid":2315629,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:23:07.000Z","msg":"又變種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f66a8ddc8ec275d564735eb051c3778b5c96410","tid":2315629,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:27:00.000Z","msg":"說好的廢老殺手大洗牌呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523a62aad48c4311427b74ad1207ab03fabca996","tid":2315629,"uid":77968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:30:13.000Z","msg":"鬼咩，當你老到7、80歲嗰陣仲有心有力跳舞？呢啲病毒根本就係富人恩物，共用概念嘅天敵尅星。"},{"pid":"eae451de184c8115bab963935f5ffc43094706cf","tid":2315629,"uid":4349,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"希望講just a flu 果班連登仔用生命演示一次真係流料"},{"pid":"6ad67a02bf